[The Blade of Romance]

2
00:00:08,010 --> 00:00:11,010
[Episode 7]

3
00:00:11,270 --> 00:00:12,080
Your Majesty,

4
00:00:12,250 --> 00:00:14,240
let me accompany you to the hot springs.

5
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,510
It gets cold here in the winter.

6
00:00:15,510 --> 00:00:17,280
You must take care of your health.

7
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:18,540
You're so thoughtful.

8
00:00:19,030 --> 00:00:21,960
I really wish I had a daughter.

9
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:32,030
[Wen Rou]

10
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,880
[Do you like the gift]

11
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,930
[I gave you?]

12
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,470
Your Majesty.

13
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,530
It seems there’s some noise
coming from inside.

14
00:00:41,530 --> 00:00:43,730
I'm afraid someone might be in trouble.

15
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:45,210
Let's go check it out.

16
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:06,430
Zhiyuan.

17
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,070
[How is this possible?]

18
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:11,330
[Why is Zhiyuan here?]

19
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:18,070
Third Prince,

20
00:01:18,070 --> 00:01:19,920
why are you coming out from there?

21
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,950
Isn't this Wen Rou's hot spring pool?

22
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:23,150
Rou is in poor health.

23
00:01:23,710 --> 00:01:25,770
The maid said she fainted in the pool.

24
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,530
As her brother,

25
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:31,640
it's only natural that
I came to look after her.

26
00:01:31,850 --> 00:01:33,710
It’s good to care for your sister,

27
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,460
but you should know your boundaries.

28
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,440
After all,

29
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:39,470
men and women are different.

30
00:01:39,509 --> 00:01:41,110
Your Majesty, you are right.

31
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:42,410
I'll take Rou back now.

32
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:45,570
Zhiyuan.

33
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,290
Hot.

34
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,280
I'm so hot.

35
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,500
Who are you?

36
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:27,750
Help me.

37
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:31,590
Rou.

38
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,170
I'll get you some water.

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:43,960
Rou.

40
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:45,400
Calm down.

41
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,360
She's lost her mind.

42
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:02,110
She doesn't recognize me at all.

43
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:03,180
Rou,

44
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:03,960
be good.

45
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:15,870
The aphrodisiac is extremely evil.

46
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:18,840
It's designed to
destroy a woman's chastity.

47
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,210
If I don't help her,

48
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:22,870
she will certainly die.

49
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:23,800
Please help me.

50
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:26,590
Weiwei.

51
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,560
Zhiyuan.

52
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,840
Zhiyuan.

53
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,269
Do you know what you were doing?

54
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,560
How dare you harm her?

55
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:26,360
I won't kill you,

56
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,390
but you'll pay

57
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,590
for what you've done.

58
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:30,560
Zhiyuan.

59
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,460
How have you become like this?

60
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,870
We grew up together.

61
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,600
We're childhood sweethearts.

62
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,950
We're betrothed.

63
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,360
I love you so much.

64
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,640
How could you treat me like this?

65
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,310
The betrothal was arranged by Father.

66
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:46,110
All you want is to be the empress.

67
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:46,970
If tomorrow

68
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,159
Father names someone else
as the crown prince,

69
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,890
will you still want to marry me?

70
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,340
No.

71
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:54,480
That’s not true, Zhiyuan.

72
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,210
Listen to me.

73
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,000
Yan Chu.

74
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,190
Take her away.

75
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:02,680
Zhiyuan.

76
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,450
You can't do this to me.

77
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,700
Have some water.

78
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,630
My head hurts a bit.

79
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,130
Let me see

80
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,300
if you have a fever.

81
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,890
Please help me.

82
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:06,800
What exactly

83
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,480
did I do last night?

84
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:13,880
Rou,

85
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,530
you were drugged with
the knockout drops yesterday.

86
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,050
Knockout drops?

87
00:06:21,910 --> 00:06:23,200
But we still shouldn't...

88
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,270
We are siblings.

89
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:25,430
We actually...

90
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,290
Your Highness.

91
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:27,670
Your Highness.

92
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:30,330
His Majesty requests
your immediate presence.

93
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,120
Rou,

94
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:32,720
get some rest.

95
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:35,070
I'll be back soon.

96
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,720
Have Qiuhe come and
take care of the Princess.

97
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,270
Yes, Sir.

98
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,830
[How could this happen?]

99
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,010
Brother,

100
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,070
I need some time alone.

101
00:07:21,670 --> 00:07:22,740
I will come back.

102
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,680
Don't worry.
